ProductInfo.Features:
This unlocked cell phone is compatible with GSM carriers like AT&T; and T-Mobile. Not all carrier features may be supported. It will not work with CDMA carriers like Verizon Wireless, Alltel and Sprint.
International version unlocked quad-band GSM cell phone compatible with 850/900/1800/1900 frequencies and International 3G compatibility via 900/2100 UMTS plus GPRS/EDGE data capabilities
Access to corporate/personal email; QWERTY keyboard; Wi-Fi networking; Bluetooth stereo music; 2-megapixel camera/camcorder
Up to 11 hours of talk time, up to 430 hours (18 days) of standby time
What's in the Box: handset, battery, charger, wired headset, user and quick start guides
ProductInfo.Name: Nokia E63 Unlocked Cell Phone with 2 MP Camera, International 3G, Wi-Fi, Media Player, MicroSD Slot--International Version with No Warranty (Ruby Red)
